# A Set of Tutorials for the LAMMPS Simulation Package (LiveCoMS, 2025)
# By Simon Gravelle, Cecilia M. S. Alvares, Jacob R. Gissinger, and Axel Kohlmeyer
# Please cite doi.org/10.33011/livecoms.6.1.3037
# Find more on GitHub: https://github.com/lammpstutorials

units metal
boundary p p p
log cracking_performance.log
atom_style full
pair_style vashishta
neighbor 1.0 bin
neigh_modify delay 1

read_data generate.data

pair_coeff * * SiO.1990.vashishta Si O

#dump viz all image 250 myimage-*.ppm type type &
  #shiny 0.1 box no 0.01 view 180 90 zoom 3.0 size 1800 600
#dump_modify viz backcolor white &
  #acolor Si yellow adiam Si 2.5 &
  #acolor O red adiam O 2

thermo 250
thermo_style custom step temp etotal vol density

dump ovito_dump all custom 250 cracking_traj.lammpstrj id type element x y z
dump_modify ovito_dump element Si O

timestep 0.001
fix nvt1 all nvt temp 300 300 0.1
fix mydef all deform 1 x erate 0.005
run 50000

write_data cracking.data
